data.description: Gorgeous modern 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home, built in 2019; wood laminate flooring, open floor plan, featuring all-white kitchen with stainless steel appliances; peninsula style counter with quartz countertops, and tons of storage space. Relax at your cozy patio with outdoor ceiling fan. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms including the master suite with ensuite bathroom plus a loft. Led lights all throughout the home; The home includes a Sunpower leased solar system and 220v for charging 2 electric cars in the garage. Few minutes walk to school and groceries, shops.  Refrigerator, washer and dryer all included in the sale.
